ABOUT


This pre owned, 2002 Omega Seamaster Chrono Diver 2598.20 is in like new condition and comes as a full set, with additional 1 year warranty from The Watch Village.




All of our watches undergo a thorough inspection of accuracy, functionality and condition to meet our strict standards. Additionally, we check each watch against records to ensure authenticity and ownership status.




Becoming increasingly rare to find in such good condition, this classic Seamaster features a crisp white dial with famed wave patten. The stand out orange sub-hands give this dial a much needed pop of colour and contrast well with the all steel case and bezel construction. The bezel is unidirectional and features an engraved diving scale with navy painted markers. All presented on a brushed and polished stainless steel bracelet and powered by the Omega Calibre 1164 automatic chronometer movement.




Model wears watch on 7 ¼” wrist
